          rel="noopener noreferrer">Docs</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Please report issues or feature requests via
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ryotahagihara/astro-tailwind-starter/issues"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        GitHub Issues</a
      >.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Credits</h2>
    <p>
      This template includes a "Built with
      <a
        href="https://github.com/ryotahagihara/astro-tailwind-starter"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">astro-tailwind-starter</a
      >" link in the footer. Keeping it is optional but greatly appreciated! It
      helps others discover this template and supports the project.
    </p>
  </section>

